snippet.title: Bluearchive Collaboration OST Piano Performance (M/V) / 「A Certain Scientific Railgun T」
snippet.description:
Blue Archive Collaboration OST  - 「To Aru Kagaku no railgun T」 Piano Performance


Hello everyone, today's performance is the theme song from the latest collaboration event "Youth Record of a Certain Science" held in Japan server.

“A Certain Scientific Railgun,” which is the original work of the collaboration,
It is a work that many people say is a fundamental cartoon that dominated an era.
This theme song is well made with a nostalgic sensibility from that time.

Thank you for listening.
---------------------------------------------------
Discord Channel : https://discord.gg/TGvwJR9rs7
Twitch Streaming : https://www.twitch.tv/frost_piano
---------------------------------------------------
「Gregorius」 Piano Epic Performance (Full Ver.) : https://youtu.be/2Gn1mqF0OEc
4th PV 「RE Aoharu」 Piano & KR Ver. (Subtitled) : https://youtu.be/WWYLDYWWhHI
Blue Archive Memorial BGM 「Midnight Trip」 Piano Play : https://youtu.be/VLaDJCDIA8Q
Blue Archive 1st Anniversary PV OST(Luminous Memory) Piano Play : https://youtu.be/1xhW91bbFS8
---------------------------------------------------
템플릿 : 론박자막연구소
---------------------------------------------------
